{
  "stem": "1568.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The following morning, I guess to prove to us, they send about four people or six people into the ghetto with a German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I, this-- what were I then-- 14-year-old kid, 12, 13, 14-year-old kid, walked in this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like a morgue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You didn't see a person in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All you saw was the Ukrainians because the Ukrainians did the dirty work over there in the brown uniforms throughout the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We walked to the place where I saw my mom's sister who-- with some other people from the other working people who were there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I assured them that what the German told us, that not to worry that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they'll be saved and after that, we'll be all together.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as we walked back to our working place, still I can remember I had an uncle who was a photographer and an artist, who it happens that the picture that you're going to see, he's the one who made it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just happened to have a little daughter, three years old, saw me and she says, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have two Leicas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, Leica was the best camera then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll give them to you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can you save me?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here, that little boy me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well anyway, things like this stay in memory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why-- why do you think he asked you that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why do you think he thought you might--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saw me with a German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saw me-- nobody else could walk on the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He saw me walking in the street with a German and he felt that I had some influence or some power to do it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's just like anybody picking in the straw.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
